{"tid":42334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"26少女歲失蹤，要報警？","createTime":"2016-12-16T14:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T17:15:12.000Z","uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e8dc672abb1db3318fadc00d187d1a787b1e799","tid":42334,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:54:39.000Z","msg":"12月16日(五) 19:10<br />\n少女黃麗慧失蹤　警籲市民幫幫手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j34DnJH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj34DnJH.jpg&h=beb3639f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n失蹤女子黃麗慧。<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=A4g5XuAtNWp4SMA9AX0EIQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=64f3e483\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a> 東網專訊】26歲少女黃麗慧，在本周三下午獨自離開天水圍天恆邨住所後便告失蹤，家人昨日向警方報案。黃身高約1.6米，體重約45公斤，瘦身材，尖面型，黃皮膚及蓄啡長直髮。她最後露面時身穿灰色外套，綠色長裙，白色運動鞋及攜有白色手袋。她後頸、右腳踝及右上臂有紋身圖案。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲任何人如有該失蹤女子的消息或曾見過她，請致電3661 3112或6273 5787或電郵至rmpu-ntn-1@police.gov.hk與新界北總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n幾靚女，宜家唔知點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bd49d29cfdda93aaa0441f43440f22c4b6788d","tid":42334,"uid":67,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:55:32.000Z","msg":"比張相嚇一嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d8204270c7c77aa9b16b78b01c8c070978c3bf","tid":42334,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f092bfb04e65753558182534773c76b2200f27b2","tid":42334,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:05:02.000Z","msg":"去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d597acefdb7ccf7ae9e8daea40c6b5bd6910b9be","tid":42334,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:07:14.000Z","msg":"有怪莫怪"},{"pid":"04d981c6744d95883cf181d7360087e8d0efb4a4","tid":42334,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:17:33.000Z","msg":"26仲少女?<br />\n點解失蹤唔報得警"},{"pid":"df184b8e09f78613acd496765a0621c178476c19","tid":42334,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T16:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比張相嚇一嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n張相係咪P過?"},{"pid":"c545de683e2b9ec2bad711a5caa2948810551e9d","tid":42334,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T16:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比張相嚇一嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e293764d4d4926ffa5bd6b423caadfc876ecca","tid":42334,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T17:07:47.000Z","msg":"鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1c2eef0c61bea545be0f14806ba0b887958a4e","tid":42334,"uid":38390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T17:15:12.000Z","msg":"&hellip;有好多積屍氣&hellip;"}]}